com.yworks.yfiles.layout.hierarchic

Class GroupingSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.hierarchic.GroupingSupport

  • public class GroupingSupport
extends Object
    This class is responsible for managing hierarchically grouped graphs.

    The grouping information is provided through IDataProviders registered with the graph with keys GroupingKeys.NODE_ID_DPKEY, GroupingKeys.PARENT_NODE_ID_DPKEY and GroupingKeys.GROUP_DPKEY.

    See Also:
    GroupingSupport, GroupingKeys
